title: Nordo in for PA!
description: Eric Nordquist fills in for PA and welcomes a cavalcade of guests including Wild Head Coach Bruce Boudreau, the Wild Radio Network's Kevin Falness, The Athletic's Britt Robson, UMD Men's Hockey Head Coach Scott Sandelin and Aaron Gleeman!
